comments: Ibaka (TOR) legally firms up in Fox's (SAC) path and does not deliver contact.
Holmes (SAC) makes contact with Ibaka's (TOR) arm and affects his shot attempt.
Anunoby (TOR) maintains a legal guarding position while contesting Bogdanovic's (SAC) jump shot.
After Lowry (TOR) establishes himself in a legal picking position in Barnes' (SAC) path, Barnes makes marginal contact.
Barnes (SAC) collapses his forearm as he guides Siakam's (TOR) body and does not affect his driving shot attempt.
Powell (TOR) maintains a legal guarding position while contesting Fox's (SAC) jump shot.
Barnes (SAC) briefly engages with Lowry (TOR) during the pick.
Lowry (TOR) establishes himself in a legal picking position in Barnes' (SAC) path and does not deliver contact.
During the drive, Fox (SAC) maintains a legal guarding position and absorbs the contact from Siakam (TOR).
Holmes (SAC) makes contact with Siakam's (TOR) arm and affects his ability to pass.
Holmes (SAC) establishes himself in a legal picking position in Anunoby's (TOR) path.
Ibaka (SAC) makes slight contact with Bogdanovic's (SAC) arm after the release that does not affect his jump shot attempt.
Powell (TOR) is not in a legal guarding position when his body makes contact with Fox's (SAC) arm and affects his shot attempt near the basket.
Lowry (TOR) establishes himself in Barnes' (SAC) path during the pick and does not deliver contact.
Bazemore (SAC) retreats and collapses his forearm when the contact occurs to Siakam (TOR) during his driving shot attempt. Bazemore doesn't deliver or extend his forearm.
Holmes (SAC) is established in Powell's (TOR) path during the off-ball screen and makes marginal contact.
Anunoby (TOR) maintains a legal guarding position while defending Fox's (SAC) jump shot attempt.
Holmes (SAC) commits a take foul on Siakam (TOR).
Ibaka (TOR) does not maintain a legal vertical defensive position as he turns and delivers contact to Holmes (SAC) during his layup.
Bazemore (SAC) commits a take foul on Anunoby (TOR).
Holmes (SAC) establishes a legal screening position in Lowry's (TOR) path and slightly extends his arms as the screen concludes.
Holmes (SAC) establishes himself in Ibaka's (TOR) path during the pick and makes marginal contact.
Ibaka (TOR) maintains a legal guarding position while defending Bjelica's (SAC) jump shot attempt.
Bogdanovic (SAC) commits a take foul on Powell (TOR).
Lowry (TOR) maintains a legal guarding position while defending Bazemore's (SAC) jump shot attempt.
